# Your Anthropic API key — for local development only.
#
# Security notes:
#   - For local dev: setting this here is fine. The dev server is not public-facing.
#   - For Vercel deploy: set this in the Vercel dashboard (Settings → Environment Variables),
#     not here. Vite embeds VITE_* vars into the compiled JS bundle at build time,
#     so a deployed site with this key set is readable in the page source.
#     Keep your deployed URL private — do not share it as a public app.
#   - If this is unset, the UI prompts for the key at runtime. The key lives in
#     component state only and is never written to localStorage or sent to any
#     server other than Anthropic's API directly.
#
# Get your key: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Web search (web_search_20250305) must be enabled on the key for live mode to work.

VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
